OL,3,CTrump tells Starmer: We don't need
OL,4,Cpeople that join wars after we've
OL,5,Calready won
OL,7,FDonald Trump has hit out at Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer over the Iran conflict, saying
OL,9,F"we don't need people that join wars
OL,10,Fafter we've already won".
OL,12,FIt comes after the Ministry of Defence
OL,13,Fsaid it was increasing the
OL,14,Fpreparedness of HMS Prince of Wales
OL,15,Fand reducing the time it would take to
OL,16,Fdeploy.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
