OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772993165
OL,3,CTrump tells Starmer: We don't need
OL,4,Cpeople that join wars after we've
OL,5,Calready won
OL,7,FThe US President posted on his Truth
OL,8,FSocial platform: "The United Kingdom,
OL,9,Four once Great Ally, maybe the
OL,10,FGreatest of them all, is finally
OL,11,Fgiving serious thought to sending two
OL,12,Faircraft carriers to the Middle East.
OL,14,F"That's OK, Prime Minister Starmer, we
OL,15,Fdon't need them any longer ` But we
OL,16,Fwill remember. We don't need people
OL,17,Fthat join Wars after we've already
OL,18,Fwon!"
OL,26,@pD@ROUvD@AOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
