CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772993165
OL,3,CTrump tells Starmer: We don't need
OL,4,Cpeople that join wars after we've
OL,5,Calready won
OL,7,FNo 10 issued the following statement
OL,8,Fin response: "As Keir Starmer said
OL,9,Fearlier this week: 'President Trump
OL,10,Fhas expressed his disagreement with
OL,11,Four decision not to get involved in
OL,12,Fthe initial strikes, but it is my duty
OL,13,Fto judge what is in Britain's national
OL,14,Finterest. That is what I have done,
OL,15,Fand I stand by it.'"
OL,17,FThe post comes amid mounting tension
OL,18,Fbetween the two countries over
OL,19,FStarmer's decision not to join the
OL,20,Finitial US-Israel strikes on Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
