OL,3,CTrump tells Starmer: We don't need
OL,4,Cpeople that join wars after we've
OL,5,Calready won
OL,7,FThe UK has since agreed to allow the
OL,8,FUS to use its bases for "specific
OL,9,Fdefensive operations", with B-1 bomber
OL,10,Fjets seen landing at RAF Fairford in
OL,11,FGloucestershire on Saturday.
OL,13,FThe Ministry of Defence said the US
OL,14,Fwas using the bases for "specific
OL,15,Fdefensive operations to prevent Iran
OL,16,Ffiring missiles into the region" and
OL,17,Fputting British lives at risk.
OL,26,@vD@YOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
