SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1772993165
OL,3,CTrump tells Starmer: We don't need
OL,4,Cpeople that join wars after we've
OL,5,Calready won
OL,7,FA Merlin helicopter is also being sent
OL,8,Fto the region to help with
OL,9,Fsurveillance from the air and RAF
OL,10,FTyphoon and F-35 jets are continuing
OL,11,Fair operations over Jordan, Qatar and
OL,12,FCyprus.
OL,14,FEarlier this week, the president said
OL,15,Fhe was "not happy" with Starmer over
OL,16,Fhis decision not to get involved in
OL,17,Fthe initial strikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
