OL,3,CTrump tells Starmer: We don't need
OL,4,Cpeople that join wars after we've
OL,5,Calready won
OL,7,FStarmer has faced criticism about the
OL,8,Fgovernment's approach and claims of a
OL,9,Flack of preparedness, but has insisted
OL,10,Fhe is "standing firm" on the UK's
OL,11,Fmilitary response, "despite pressure
OL,12,Fto do otherwise".
OL,14,FThe prime minister has repeatedly
OL,15,Fdefended his decision, saying he does
OL,16,Fnot believe in "regime change from the
OL,17,Fskies".
OL,19,FThis is a breaking story, more to
OL,20,Ffollow
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
